# PiKaOs — FRONTEND env (Vite). Copy to Frontend/.env if you need to override.
# PUBLIC: every VITE_* var is baked into the JS bundle and shipped to the browser — anyone can read
# it (view-source / DevTools). NEVER put a secret here; app config only. Secrets live in Backend/.env.
# Same-origin in dev via the Vite proxy (/api -> backend).
VITE_API_BASE=/api
